  "title": "WORKSHOP SUPERVISOR (COMMERCIAL)",
  "description": "<p>WORKSHOP TEAM LEADER | 2 PAX REQUIRED | IMMEDIATE START</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>📍 Location: Joo Koon MRT</p>\n<p>💰 Salary: $3,000 – $3,500/month</p>\n<p>⏰ Working Hours: 9am – 6pm (5.5 days/week)</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Job Scope: </p>\n<p>🛠 Supervise and manage daily workshop operations to ensure smooth workflow.</p>\n<p>🛠 Provide guidance, coaching, and training to staff to enhance technical skills..</p>\n<p>🛠 Identify and resolve operational issues to minimize downtime and improve productivity..</p>\n<p>🛠 Manage workshop resources, including inventory, tools, and equipment maintenance. </p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Requirements: </p>\n<p>📋 Diploma or certification in the Mechanical/Electrical field (preferred).</p>\n<p>📋 Minimum 5 years of relevant experience in workshop supervision or a similar technical role.</p>\n<p>📋 Strong leadership, organizational, and problem-solving skills.</p>\n<p><br></p>",
